[MongoDB Atlas Account: mm9, AWS Account: hps]

AWS SETUP:
1- Go to Console & Sign Up
2- Create a New User
3- Store Access Key ID, Secret Access Key and AWS Region in .env File

AWS Simple Email Service (SES):
1- Verify 2 email addresses (mm9 - admin, hps - sample user)
2- npm i aws-sdk
3- Config AWS (accessKeyId, secretAccessKey & region)
4- Create ses variable (new AWS.SES({ apiVersion: '2010-12-01' }))
5- Create params variable
6- const sendEmailOnRegister = ses.sendEmail(params).promise()
7- Add .then and .catch to resolve/reject the promise
